[show NS]South's \HKT8 was only three-deep support, and the coded minimum confessed a flat hand with no ruff in sight, so the auction stayed in 2NT rather than a heart partscore. Eight tricks came home for plus 120 — exactly the modest result a flat minimum should expect.}
