[BID Pass] ⟦You pass; 2\C is the final contract.⟧
[show NS]South's \HK65 was a flat three-card holding not worth a raise, so opener showed spades with 1\S; North's preference to clubs landed the hands in 2\C for nine tricks. Declining is as much a part of the method as raising.}
